    "description": "<p>Hiap&nbsp;Engineering &amp; Construction Pte Ltd was established in early 1990s and&nbsp;incorporated in 1998. We have a team of Licensed Gas Service Workers (LGSW) authorized by the Energy Market Authority to carry out gas service works involving gas pipe inspection, installation and maintenance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>A professional and an expert in gas with near&nbsp;to 30 years of field experience and an extensive understanding in the gas industry, We maintain a high standard of safe and proficient gas pipe services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our vast portfolio of gas engineering and pipe work projects cover premises such as Residential &amp; Commercial buildings, F&amp;B Establishments, Religious Institutions, Schools and Hotels.</p>\n<p>Our company renders services for the inspection and soundness testing of residential &amp; non-residential premises that is an annual requirement for any piped-gas consumers under the Gas&nbsp;Act.</p>",
